1. Application startup flow
         App starts 
    ---> Main Controller    :  initialize default state
    ---> UI controller      :  renders initial screen

2. PDF upload flow
         User uploads PDF
    ---> Main Controller    :  receives file event
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  extract and store file information
    ---> UI controller      :  UI updates PDF info panel

3. Question submit flow
         User submits a question(prompt)
    ---> Main Controller    :  receives file event
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  validates that PDF exists
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  user message is appended to chat state
    ---> UI controller      :  UI renders user message
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  LLM flow starts

4. LLM request flow
         MainController starts LLM response generation
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  perform LLM call (history + PDF text + user prompt)
    ---> XXXX Controller    :  appends assistant message to chat state
    ---> UI controller      :  UI updates PDF info panel


5. Error handling flow
         Any extraction or LLM operation fails
    ---> controller catches exception
    ---> UI renders error message

6. Remove PDF flow
         User clicks remove PDF
    ---> controller clears document-related state
    ---> uploader state changes
    ---> UI re-renders empty upload screen.


7. PDF replacement flow
         User uploads a different PDF
    ---> controller detects changed file hash
    ---> old document/chat state is cleared
    ---> new extraction runs
    ---> UI updates PDF info panel.

8. Clear conversation flow
         User clicks clear conversation
    ---> controller resets chat history only
    ---> UI re-renders chat area empty while keeping PDF state.

9. PDF extraction flow

10. Context-fit / truncation flow : If PDF text doe not fits context budget
